N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 202.8 - Marketing research

State Regulations

The commissioner is hereby authorized to contract with any
person, including the New York Cherry Growers Association, to carry on or cause
to be carried on marketing research or marketing study and to expend any
available monies for such purpose. Notes
